hands_on_practices.solution:
1. Volume fractions:  
   $M_i=\xi M_r$, $V_r=M_r/\rho_r$, $V_i=M_i/\rho_i=\xi M_r/\rho_i$. Total volume $V=V_r+V_i$.  

$$
     f_i=\frac{V_i}{V_r+V_i}
          =\frac{\xi/\rho_i}{1/\rho_r+\xi/\rho_i}
          =\frac{\xi\,\rho_r}{\xi\,\rho_r+\rho_i},\qquad 
     f_r=1-f_i=\frac{\rho_i}{\xi\,\rho_r+\rho_i}.
   $$

2. Effective tensile strength:  

$$
     \sigma_{eff}=\sigma_r f_r+\sigma_i f_i
                  =\frac{\sigma_r\,\rho_i+\sigma_i\,\xi\,\rho_r}
                         {\xi\,\rho_r+\rho_i}.
   $$

3. Bulk density:  

$$
     \rho=\frac{M_r+M_i}{V}
          =\frac{M_r(1+\xi)}{M_r\bigl(1/\rho_r+\xi/\rho_i\bigr)}
          =\frac{1+\xi}{1/\rho_r+\xi/\rho_i}
          =\frac{(1+\xi)\,\rho_r\,\rho_i}{\rho_i+\xi\,\rho_r}.
   $$

4. Critical specific energy:

$$
     Q_D^*=C\frac{\sigma_{eff}}{\rho}
            =C\,\frac{\frac{\sigma_r\,\rho_i+\sigma_i\,\xi\,\rho_r}
                          {\xi\,\rho_r+\rho_i}}
                   {\frac{(1+\xi)\,\rho_r\,\rho_i}{\rho_i+\xi\,\rho_r}}
            =C\,\frac{\sigma_r\,\rho_i+\sigma_i\,\xi\,\rho_r}
                   {(1+\xi)\,\rho_r\,\rho_i}.
   $$
